{"tid":2016510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳茂波: 派一萬元六月底接受申請  正聯絡飲食界推出優惠","createTime":"2020-05-14T12:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T14:07:28.000Z","uid":83713,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f279ba08bcb53d67544c228a2445b4244eaa75e5","tid":2016510,"uid":83713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:11:02.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波表示，派發一萬元的計劃下月底會接受申請，相信大部分市民會於八月收到錢，<span style=\"color: red;\">政府正與零售飲食業界商量，屆時會推出優惠，刺激消費。</span><br />\n<br />\n立法會通過財政預算案，民主派議員提出的52項修正案，包括多項削減警隊、主要官員薪酬及政府部門開支，在建制派議員反對下全部被否決。民主派不滿所有修正案被否決，建制派議員則指，對部分措施有意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391035&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391035%26refer%3DShare&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=ee2d77bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D391035%26refer%3DShare&h=4ce955c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=391035&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"8eeb4d345c8c66e1b5101db4d060f6c89efd5304","tid":2016510,"uid":18477,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>堅持黃色經濟圈</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3218c5c354d98e72a902b7c116cc1a025175cb00","tid":2016510,"uid":236232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1710187475a8348dbfd2ec66d989980c47aca3ae","tid":2016510,"uid":357636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"等睇食滿5舊平10雞優惠"},{"pid":"54dea46e0c43fdee3f0673c5f4f84b8d44cd69c3","tid":2016510,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"疫情都舒緩左咁多<br />\n果1萬蚊仲有咩用"},{"pid":"2657287cff25dfddcfcbf8bd7ede4afd8df85519","tid":2016510,"u